{"ID":"20231121095322-1ux31zd","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"1f958","id":"20231121095322-1ux31zd","scroll":"\u0026#123;\u0026quot;rootId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20231121095322-1ux31zd\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;startId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20231121095327-151lz8a\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;endId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20231121095322-6cw4e1l\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;scrollTop\u0026quot;:0,\u0026quot;focusId\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;20231121095327-151lz8a\u0026quot;,\u0026quot;focusStart\u0026quot;:0,\u0026quot;focusEnd\u0026quot;:0\u0026#125;","title":"项目原理","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231121095327-151lz8a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231121095327-151lz8a","updated":"20231215151456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"基于python 实现语音识别文字"}]},{"ID":"20231215151456-hzkq4xb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215151456-hzkq4xb","updated":"20231215151521"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实现文字情感分析和语义解析"}]},{"ID":"20231215151514-h7lyfxj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215151514-h7lyfxj","updated":"20231215151514"}},{"ID":"20231215151412-m8algwl","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20231215151412-m8algwl","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20231215152021-lfue8nf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-lfue8nf","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"语音识别为文字，即自动语音识别（Automatic Speech Recognition, ASR），是通过计算机算法将人类说出的语音转换为可读的文字形式。这一过程主要分为几个步骤："}]},{"ID":"20231215152021-tqfcxpn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-tqfcxpn","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231215152021-3oa3ale","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-3oa3ale","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231215152021-9xymxsc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-9xymxsc","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"声音信号采集"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：\n通过麦克风等设备捕获声音信号。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231215152021-x5sxtgm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-x5sxtgm","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231215152021-f3hmqbw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-f3hmqbw","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"预处理"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：\n这一步可能包括去噪、回声消除、增益调整等，以提高后续处理阶段的准确性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231215152021-2h2muee","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-2h2muee","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231215152021-wtql9pq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-wtql9pq","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"特征提取"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：\n从原始音频中提取关键特征，如梅尔频率倒谱系数（Mel Frequency Cepstral Coefficients, MFCCs）、线性预测编码（Linear Predictive Coding, LPC）等，这些特征能更好地描述语音的本质属性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231215152021-9vcya83","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-9vcya83","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231215152021-b5br99g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-b5br99g","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语音识别模型"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：\n使用机器学习或深度学习模型对特征进行分析和解码，常见的有隐马尔科夫模型（Hidden Markov Models, HMMs）、深度神经网络（Deep Neural Networks, DNNs）、循环神经网络（Recurrent Neural Networks, RNNs）、长短时记忆网络（Long Short-Term Memory, LSTM）、门控循环单元（Gated Recurrent Units, GRUs）、卷积神经网络（Convolutional Neural Networks, CNNs）以及Transformer架构等。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231215152021-w4j6y02","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-w4j6y02","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231215152021-yz043sd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-yz043sd","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"解码和输出"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"：\n将模型的输出转换为可理解的文本，并使用语言模型优化结果，例如考虑语法和上下文信息。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20231215152021-c3a22t1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-c3a22t1","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"现在的主流技术主要是基于深度学习的方法，特别是在近几年，端到端的神经网络模型已经成为了研究和应用的焦点。这些模型能够直接从输入的音频波形映射到输出的文本序列，中间不再需要传统的特征提取和声学模型-语言模型联合解码的过程。常用的端到端模型包括CTC（Connectionist Temporal Classification）、LAS（Listen Attend and Spell）、Transformer以及RNN-T（Recurrent Neural Network Transducer）等。"}]},{"ID":"20231215152021-i7gwldn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231215152021-i7gwldn","updated":"20231215152021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在开源框架方面，Kaldi、K2、PaddleSpeech、ESPnet、WeNet都是当前比较流行的ASR解决方案。而针对产品落地，会根据应用场景的需求选择合适的方案，比如考虑到资源占用、实时性、准确率等因素。"}]}]},{"ID":"20231121095322-6cw4e1l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231121095322-6cw4e1l","updated":"20231121095322"}}]}